name: Leviticus-X
description:
Saturn's top scientist Dr. Zeto developed Leviticus as a prototype jet pack for their scout teams that were being sent to the farthest reaches of the galaxy. 

This jet pack is made out of unique lightweight alloy that is also very flexible which allows it to become very compact when not in use but once. Once fully deployed it has some of the most advanced tech allowing it to read atmospheric, weather, gravity and a myriad of other data to adjust to any planets condition. 

Depending on the conditions it will adapt to using jet-fuel, magnetic levitation, or hydro jets to propel itself around any given planet. An item for the ultimate space explorer.

Speed: +10
Armor: +5
